The paper deals with facial expression recognition using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves a combination of generative, contrastive, and discriminative models, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also uses publicly available face expression databases, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper involves end-to-end training of deep neural networks, which is a common topic in neural networks (cs.NE).
